.DT
disallow_save
$MUDNAME$ Creator Help
disallow_save

.SH Name
.SP 5 5
disallow_save -  This method stops the player from being able to save.
.EP

.SH Syntax
.SI 5
void disallow_save()
.EI

.SH Defined in
.SI 5
/global/player.c
.EI

.SH Description
.SP 5 5

This method stops the player from being able to save.  This is done while
the inventory is regenerating to stop problems with inventory loss due
to logging off before it has finished.
.EP

.SH See also
.SP 5 5
allow_save(), query_save_inhibit()

.EP

